AttributeList.Text:
================================================================================ This module is used everywhere one alarm shall be generated when one security input becomes False. The alarm can be True only when the input Enable Alarm is also True. When the condition to generate the alarm is not fullfilled, a boolean output is available to inform the upper level that the alarm can be reset. The alarm is reset by means of the AlarmResetPB signal.
This module generates also a word containing all necessary information for HMI Icon animation, and a word with all information for HMI safety module diagnostic screen. ================================================================================
